      <title class="- topic/title ">
         <ph class="- topic/ph " props="autonumber">52.213-2</ph> Invoices.</title>
      <conbody outputclass="clause" class="- topic/body concept/conbody ">
         <p class="- topic/p " id="d3165e8">As prescribed in <ph outputclass="ClauseProvisionXREF" class="- topic/ph ">
               <xref href="13.302-5.dita#FAR_13_302_5"
                     base="i1111549"
                     outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                     class="- topic/xref ">13.302-5</xref>(b)</ph>, insert the following clause:</p>
         <p class="- topic/p " outputclass="Ctr_SmCaps" id="d3165e15">Invoices <ph outputclass="SmCaps" class="- topic/ph ">(Apr 1984)</ph>
         </p>
         <p class="- topic/p ">The Contractorâ€™s invoices must be submitted before payment can be made. The Contractor will be paid on the basis of the invoice, which must state-</p>
         <ol id="d3130e28" class="- topic/ol ">
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d3165e23">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(a)</ph>
						            The starting and ending dates of the subscription delivery; and</p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d3165e28">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(b)</ph>
						            Either that orders have been placed in effect for the addressees required, or that the orders will be placed in effect upon receipt of payment.</p>
            </li>
         </ol>
         <p class="- topic/p " outputclass="Endofclause">(End of clause)</p>
